# Cal.com Integration
#
# The app uses the KEYLESS Cal.com embed (@calcom/embed-react). No API key is
# required and none should be committed — Vite inlines VITE_* values into the
# client bundle, so a real key would be publicly exposed.
#
# The booking links are configured directly in code as constants:
#   src/components/estimator/MeetingScheduler.tsx
#     CAL_LINK_15 = "hisham-khalid-qyohid/15min"
#     CAL_LINK_30 = "hisham-khalid-qyohid/30min"
#
# To change the Cal.com handle or event types, edit those constants.
# There are no required environment variables for the booking feature.
